node.text:
Tonight’s quick core with the stability ball! 
30 sec on/10sec off x3-4 rounds of each move
*Ball Pass
*Knee Tucks
*Plank Leans 
*Twists 
*Straight Leg Sit Ups
#coreworkout #core #abstrengthening #abs #core #stabilityball #coreonthefloor #homeworkout #fitness #workout #strength #personaltrainer #mkehome
